phy: allwinner: add phy driver for USB3 PHY on Allwinner H6 SoC

Allwinner H6 SoC contains a USB3 PHY (with USB2 DP/DM lines also
controlled).

Add a driver for it.

The register operations in this driver is mainly extracted from the BSP
USB3 driver.

